snippet.title: Get Tanked! Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Early Access out now!

STEAM ▶ https://store.steampowered.com/app/1679800/Get_Tanked/?utm_source=yt

Get Tanked! is an adrenaline-filled arena shooter with tanks that can double jump, boost, and rotate midair. Use power ups to outplay your enemies in creative ways. Dive into insane, dynamic fights and have a blast playing locally or online.
